# Change Log

All notable changes to this project are documented in this file.

The project currently has no tagged releases. Entries therefore follow the dates on which changes were integrated. New entries should be added to the `Unreleased` section and moved into a dated section when they are published on `master`.

## Unreleased

### Added

- Central change log for user-visible features, security fixes and relevant maintenance work.

## 2026-07-11

### Added

- Automated execution of the dependency-free JavaScript regression test suite in the project workflow.

### Changed

- Established the `develop` branch as the integration stage before changes are released to `master`.

## 2026-07-10

### Security

- Hardened the local regular-expression safety heuristics against inefficient and potentially excessive backtracking.
- Reworked ambiguous repeated alternatives so escaped characters and ordinary characters are matched by disjoint branches.
- Added documentation for the full regular-expression checks and resolved the associated CodeQL findings.

## 2026-06-07

### Added

- YAML/Properties converter for Java-style configuration files.
- Dependency-free Node.js regression tests for the converter and responsive regex controls.
- ROT13 as an additional encoding and decoding algorithm.
- Browser-generated offline ZIP containing the complete static application.
- `AGENTS.md` with binding mobile-first and offline architecture guidelines.
- Compact navigation hints for tools.

### Changed

- Reworked the interface to follow a mobile-first layout with touch-friendly controls and improved handling of narrow viewports.
- Improved the Base64/ROT13 interface with a dedicated algorithm selector and explanatory descriptions.
- Renamed the YAML/Properties tool to the more general label `Konverter`.
- Improved converter behavior when changing direction, swapping input and output, clearing fields or processing empty input.
- Moved the keyboard shortcut hint next to the search field.
- Split offline ZIP generation into a dedicated module.
- Updated the README with offline usage, privacy guarantees, included tools and test instructions.

### Security

- Removed remote regular-expression checks and runtime CDN dependencies.
- Replaced external ReDoS analysis with local browser-based heuristics.
- Ensured that regular expressions and test data remain on the user's device.

### Accessibility

- Improved status announcements and feedback in the converter.
- Increased touch target sizes and improved wrapping and scrolling for long content.
- Linked the site brand to the GitHub repository with appropriate accessible labeling.

## 2026-03-08

### Fixed

- Corrected and stabilized the regular-expression tools after their initial introduction.

## 2026-03-06

### Added

- Regular-expression comparison tool for a deliberately restricted regular subset.

## 2026-03-04

### Added

- Initial static application structure and user interface.
- Cron expression explainer.
- Base64 encoder and decoder.
- Regular-expression checker.
- GitHub Pages compatible, browser-native operation without a build step.

---

This change log is maintained in reverse chronological order and focuses on changes relevant to users, security and project operation. Minor wording, formatting and internal refactoring changes may be omitted.